  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">In the system of equations below, <span class=\"italic\">a</span> and <span class=\"italic\">c</span> are constants.<p class=\"stem_paragraph \"><span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"Equation 1: one half x, plus one third y, equals one sixth. Equation 2: a, x, plus y equals c\"></span></span></p><p class=\"stem_paragraph \">If the system of equations has an infinite number of solutions <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"x comma y \"></span></span>, what is the value of <span class=\"italic\">a</span> ?</p><p>&nbsp;</p></p>\n",
